videoSnippet.title: Tal Baron Checkmates Magnus Carlsen with a Pawn!
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Original footage of the game. Game against Carlsen starts at 1:35
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_pOsPy_iRxE

"Tal Baron explains why he used an engine to catch a cheater back in 2015"  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ahkp9y9BVEg

Tal Baron vs Magnus Carlsen
A blitz game on ICC
Nimzo-Indian Defense: Kmoch Variation (E20)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. f3 d5 5. a3 Bxc3+ 6. bxc3 c5 7. cxd5 exd5 8. e3 O-O 9. Bd3 b6 10. Ne2 Ba6 11. O-O Re8 12. Ng3 Bxd3 13. Qxd3 Nc6 14. Bb2 h5 15. e4 h4 16. Nf5 dxe4 17. fxe4 Nxe4 18. Qf3 cxd4 19. Nh6+ gxh6 20. Qxf7+ Kh8 21. cxd4 Qg5 22. Rae1 Qg7 23. Qxg7+ Kxg7 24. d5+ Kg6 25. dxc6 Rac8 26. Rf4 Nc5 27. Rf6+ Kg5 28. Ref1 h3 29. Bc1+ Kg4 30. Rg6+ Kh5 31. Rxh6+ Kg4 32. gxh3#
